Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.13,0:01:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美的星星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.80,0:01:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.93,0:01:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tim，總有一天會有人從那片星海中來迎接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.67,0:01:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來迎接我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.80,0:01:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯．這片星空上的某個地方有個很想念你的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.41,0:01:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢，Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.82,0:02:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第七話 試練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.15,0:02:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位是Timothy•Constance先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.69,0:02:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l3歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.62,0:02:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生于Primavera行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.59,0:02:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其母是Marianne•Constance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.13,0:02:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他的父親是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.63,0:02:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ablert•Rosenfelt
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.47,0:02:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ablert•Rosenfelt，最近去世的Rosenfelt財團族長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenfelt財團？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.14,0:02:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總資産占全銀河系金融總額的6.82%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.01,0:02:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最新的統計顯示爲7.14%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.78,0:02:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦～那他是大少爺囉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timothy•Constance先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albert先生留下了遺言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.03,0:02:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指定他爲下一任繼承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.53,0:02:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過必須在指定的期限內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.16,0:02:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在特定的地方確認是他本人 這件事情才算成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.74,0:02:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以標準時間來看的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.90,0:02:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有36小時l3分58秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.67,0:03:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果無法確認的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼承的資格就會被取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～那多可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後有關係的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.28,0:03:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會爲了事業、權力展開爭奪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該要同時通知指定地點的所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.52,0:03:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是因爲資料受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導致無法辨識正確地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經故意對外放出假消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.63,0:03:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但金融管理局似乎在背後進行了一些動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的特別任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.80,0:03:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是在修復的情報中找出原本被指定的行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.37,0:03:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在期限之內將Constance先生平安送達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以當成綫索的只有這些嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DNA鑒定之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.02,0:03:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在Albert•Rosenfelt所誕生的行星…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere 怎麽樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.59,0:03:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在用網絡搜尋中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.26,0:03:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找個人情報是很不容易的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.43,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 本來就不可能太簡單吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.80,0:04:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,且是上流社會的人的話那就更是難上加難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用緊張喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.71,0:04:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Constance先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會好好保住你的遺産繼承權的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要叫我“先生”好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像不是我的名字似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.88,0:04:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boldor星系…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.89,0:04:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farandole行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在銀河系的另一端呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要經過空間跳躍一瞬間就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.41,0:04:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貧困的男孩子在魔法棒下搖身變成大富翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～好浪漫哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.61,0:04:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是最近看過的故事書一樣耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我們也走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.72,0:04:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是跟丟的話 可是會被念個半死的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私奔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸爲了跟媽媽結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.23,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放弃了繼承權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.87,0:05:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經一度脫離了Ronsenfelt財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.64,0:05:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後在Primavera行星從事農業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸用的是本名Cillford
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.28,0:05:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但最後父親還是留下了我跟媽媽回家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.72,0:05:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承襲Albert之名成爲家族之主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我連父親的容貌也不記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.03,0:05:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道自己跟Ronsenfelt家族有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從媽媽去世以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直在爺爺的農場工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.93,0:05:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 最近GOTT來了消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才第一次聽爺爺談起這件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.58,0:05:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 也真是個任性的父親呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都放著你們母子不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等有了萬一 又希望你能够繼承他的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.95,0:05:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够囉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.92,0:06:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 還讓你在GOTT或金融管理局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些大人們之間被叫來喚去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像搞錯地點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽會？搜尋的結果確實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏真的是你父親的出生地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.29,0:06:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只知道爸爸的名字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸改用Albert這個名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.67,0:06:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是跟我和媽媽分開之後的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albert幷不是我爸爸 而是陌生人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.64,0:06:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.61,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sylvia星系的…Silvana行星？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是Tim的父親成爲第25代族長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼承Albert之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.49,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幷被認定爲財團繼承人的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.02,0:07:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩兩個標準小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勉勉强强呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隕石群接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臨時形成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.47,0:07:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的偶然呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 警告意味很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.27,0:07:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是繞遠路的話就會來不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.18,0:07:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.08,0:07:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.65,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.75,0:07:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 男孩子就得這樣才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.39,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.96,0:07:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回避！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.66,0:07:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麽？剛剛那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cesario
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小Lumi、小Ec
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別這樣叫我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.08,0:08:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小Ec 就是小Ec呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.32,0:08:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 隨便你啦 他們是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola跟Cesario
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.79,0:08:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她們倆人的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你們倆個怎麽會來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是局長拜托我們偷偷保護你們的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.16,0:08:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隕石交給我們的Fenice掃除掉就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們快點去Silvana
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.90,0:08:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的多謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.07,0:08:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係、沒關係 不過你們之後得請客喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？又得請？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？中國菜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意大利菜比較好啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前不也是吃中國菜嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.72,0:08:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就决定吃意大利菜好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.59,0:08:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好期待、好期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.66,0:08:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們還是老樣子一點都沒變耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我們永遠都相親相愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.36,0:08:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小Lumi跟小Ec也很要好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是比不上我跟Cesario
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.20,0:08:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人是挺不錯 只是很會精打細算罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.53,0:09:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麽說呢…我覺得GOTT的人應該是更…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以爲我們是那種讓人不能不綳緊神經的人 是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各種人都有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是GOTT或是這世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.85,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了如果無法决定繼承人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.76,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將由我們委員會全權負責今後的運營
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.49,0:09:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.63,0:09:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在獵戶座腕部區的經營收支這期也有盈餘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.63,0:09:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因爲那個區域的負責人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代代都是由我們家的人所擔任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.04,0:09:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經由這次的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.17,0:09:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該能在財務掌管這方面獲得更多的權責吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.24,0:09:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鏘～鏘～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.08,0:09:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenfelt財團的繼承人到達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個隔間是幹嘛用的呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛生防護罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛生防護罩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,監定完畢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timothy•Constance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經過確認 證實與
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albert•Rosenfelt以及Marianne Constance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.10,0:10:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人的DNA排序一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 事情應該會更沒完沒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.84,0:10:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看來是趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.24,0:10:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來似乎正在舉行宴會的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.85,0:10:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對一定會再發生一些事情吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就等著瞧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.50,0:11:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.21,0:11:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就吃不到料理了呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.67,0:11:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“貴族階級”是以完全未接受過\N“身體適應處理”爲傲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純粹血統主義者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenfelt家族也是其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.85,0:11:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這些人對他們來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過算是雜菌而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.75,0:11:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timothy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.29,0:11:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後將在這些人之中生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽馬？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.96,0:11:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然騎馬是婦女們的嗜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但以機械馬競速 可是我們一族的傳統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.84,0:11:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是族裏的男性 沒有人不會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.37,0:11:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機械馬是一項能測試出勇氣與智慧的競賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.18,0:12:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請務必讓我們拜見一下新統帥者的技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.58,0:12:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可、可是我對機械馬…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那真是失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.75,0:12:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了你幷沒有受過貴族階級的教育
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然身爲我族的一員却在邊境的開發中行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.66,0:12:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被庶民的女孩給騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但遺傳基因是騙不了人的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.97,0:12:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我贏了賽馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.14,0:12:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們就願意承認我是繼承人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.91,0:12:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 要是贏不了的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.71,0:12:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能够自行承認自己幷沒有繼承的資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.08,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想後悔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.78,0:12:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快爲族長備馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那個必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donnersclac借你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.26,0:12:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給這些傢伙們一點顔色瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是 爲什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要理由嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說的一樣吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到參加者變的這麽多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他們都有老練的教官在指導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.82,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.22,0:13:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麽說也有我在嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.39,0:13:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像在盤算著什麽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可務必要小心提防
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.87,0:13:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.44,0:13:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯喔 再提高一點速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.91,0:13:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔…好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還蠻不賴的嘛 族長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是庶民就要像個庶民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是在受傷之前快點回家去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是幹這種小心眼的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比賽總是伴隨著危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來這是貴族的嗜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庶民是不會懂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕嗎？ 可別被甩下去了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.75,0:14:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是給過分淘氣的少爺們一點小小的懲罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害呀！Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 Mr…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對…嗯，這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友們都叫我Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.89,0:14:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0K Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.93,0:14:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tim 來了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一台也有參加嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.51,0:14:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是混在出場者之中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個完全是戰鬥用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.68,0:14:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,專業級的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你負責操縱Donner
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.21,0:14:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們讓我來負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是金融管理局的ES成員吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.72,0:14:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有隕石的歡迎儀式還不够過癮嗎？同行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身爲ES成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.26,0:15:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却還以真面目示人似乎是你們GOTT的傳統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這也是一件極度愚蠢的事情！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒙面是壞人才會做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市場可是這麽决定的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tim 噴射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.94,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donner 鋼絲腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞這種鬼玩意兒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.73,0:15:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯哦 Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.53,0:15:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是你爸爸遺傳給你的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.71,0:15:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？ Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.76,0:16:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Titano！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.53,0:16:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小Ec
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也是GOTT的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.37,0:16:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Titano的裝甲是特製的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甩他出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人如果手牽手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.46,0:16:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以控制分子的結合力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.57,0:16:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果手沒有牽上的話就不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.10,0:16:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦 Cesario、Viola
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.74,0:17:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來就等你吃意大利料理囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cesario 手…手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.72,0:17:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉呦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.39,0:17:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國菜、就吃中國菜好了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壞心眼 哼～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.91,0:17:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使擁有一個出生于開發中星球的母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.74,0:17:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也同樣能够具備勇氣 這件事你們能接受了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.18,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你父親的選擇似乎是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,委任書…就交給你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.22,0:17:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你們能瞭解就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你幫了我這麽多忙 但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.54,0:18:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…從一開始就打算這麽做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.07,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想向他們這群人討回媽媽的名譽而以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.01,0:18:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意再重新考慮一下嗎？ Timothy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.95,0:18:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是Isaac•Rosenfelt
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.42,0:18:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的祖父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖父？ 爺爺嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會…會長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您不是在靜養中嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 將你的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.90,0:18:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從你的母親身邊奪走的 正是我本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.37,0:18:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會跟你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.61,0:18:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因爲財團需要Albert的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.64,0:18:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 這麽說來 爸爸幷沒有拋弃我們母子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.48,0:18:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道Albert的遺言後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.62,0:18:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我感到相當懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.15,0:18:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的適合擔任本財團的繼承人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我覺得必須親自測試看看才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.06,0:18:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.86,0:18:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 局長早就知道指定的是哪個星球囉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.50,0:19:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒想到這些傢伙居然會如此的胡作非爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒一定得好好的懲罰懲罰他們才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.77,0:19:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎已經能够理解爸爸爲什麽會單獨回家族來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸比任何人都瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.48,0:19:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在平常環境下成長的人 要在貴族階級中生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會是件多麽辛苦的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.96,0:19:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸會離開我們母子這都是出自于爸爸對我們的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 依然指定我爲繼承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.13,0:19:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一定也是爲了讓我能够對自己的人生有選擇的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是Tim…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.31,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有權利選擇自己的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.14,0:19:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論星星告訴了你什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.35,0:19:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的道路 還是必須由你自己來决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.22,0:19:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然…我沒辦法馬上做出决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.39,0:19:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.12,0:20:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果因爲沒有族長而造成整個家族分崩離析的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不如順理繼承比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.23,0:20:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在Timothy下定决心之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼承人的問題就先保留不談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這段期間內我會先輔助族長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.20,0:20:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後萬一Timothy發生了什麽意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就立刻將Rosenfelt財團分割解體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麽辦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.05,0:20:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.08,0:20:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以慢慢考慮的Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.75,0:20:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因爲你的人生是屬于你自己的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.32,0:20:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 我覺得你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.19,0:20:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.21,0:20:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都看到了吧？ Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.87,0:20:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 希望你能好好的說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.61,0:20:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,影像證據？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.28,0:20:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.32,0:21:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金融管理局妨礙我們工作的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.59,0:21:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下子 以後我們就能牽制他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.62,0:21:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是爲了拍下這個影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.06,0:21:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才讓 Armbrust故意慫恿財團的人是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.60,0:21:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們以繼承權爲賭注展開比賽
